  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 shadow-sm mb-10">
    <p class="text-text-light mb-3">The following are examples of solutions and miscible mixtures where centrifugal separation is not effective:</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-1 text-text-light text-sm">
      <p>&bull; Salt and water</p>
      <p>&bull; Sugar and water</p>
      <p>&bull; Ink in water</p>
      <p>&bull; Diesel and gasoline</p>
      <p>&bull; Diesel and lube oil</p>
      <p>&bull; Water and glycol (antifreeze)</p>
      <p>&bull; Used oil and diesel fuel</p>
      <p>&bull; Alcohol and water</p>
      <p>&bull; Chicken fat and vegetable oil</p>
      <p>&bull; Emulsified oil and water</p>
    </div>
  </div>

