  <h2 id="can-separate-list" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-heading text-navy mb-6">Mixtures a Centrifuge Separates Effectively</h2>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 shadow-sm mb-10">
    <p class="text-text-light mb-3">Centrifuges excel at separating immiscible phases with distinct density differences:</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-1 text-text-light text-sm">
