      <p>&bull; <a href="/diesel-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Diesel from water and sludge</a></p>
      <p>&bull; Sludge from oil</p>
      <p>&bull; Fine sediment from lube oil</p>
      <p>&bull; Water from lube oil</p>
      <p>&bull; Milk fat from milk</p>
